        "action": "Require discounted water rates for unmetered single occupied properties\r\n",
        "additional_details": "A single person is likely to use less water than a larger household, so should not be required to pay the same rate.",
        "background": "We want the Government to require water companies to offer discounted water rates for properties occupied by a single person, where the property is unmetered.",
